# No unsolicited code comments

- Do not add comments to source code (including `--`, `---`, `//`, `/* */`, block docs, or inline explanations) unless the user clearly asks for comments in that request.
- Explanations, rationale, and documentation belong in chat or project docs the user requests—not in the codebase by default.
